---
title: Spiced Mushroom and Coconut Stew with cheese crostini
description: This is a fragrant dish that's packed with veg and flavoured with spices, herbs, and creamy coconut milk. The accompanying Greek style cheese crostini adds plenty of crunch for a meal that's got a little bit of everything!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R08_W45_IE_IEFQVV13545-3_Main_high-62d8b1e5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64dc86add2a77e4566ccb8fd.pdf
nutrition:
